subproject.description:
The project aims at strengthening the regulatory function of the EQA  with focus on controlling pollution of industry activities and waste which have the  potential to impact on a wide range of environmental areas including emissions to air, land and water by achieving
•	Establishing clear monitoring process and procedures including clarification of roles and responsibilities for line ministers and authorities involved in the enforcement of environmental regulations and;
•	Enhancing the capacity of the EQA environmental protection directorate regarding environmental monitoring and inspection in the areas of industrial waste and air pollution in addition to other areas that can be recommended by the consultant.

